name: Eggs
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: EGGS is an experiment in decentralized finance, the way it works is that each block, EGGS can debase by 0.001% so you will have less EGGS.  However if you place your EGGS in a Protec Single or LP staking Vault then you will get more EGGS as reward.
